   <body>
      <p>Dimensions are used to populate Dimension Sets, which are subsequently used by Guidance Rules.</p>
      <p>Dimensions can be attributes of products, quotes, quote line items, deals, and deal line items. Dimensions enable you to set the criteria which will be used to judge the quality of a deal.</p>
      <note type="note">
         <p>By default, out of the box, Line Item and Product Configuration are supported. To enable Deal Maximizer for other objects, customers should contact professional services.</p>
